GRAPH <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Digest_OperatingModelShifts> {
  <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Digest_OperatingModelShifts> a narr:Digest ;
    narr:digestOf <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#OperatingModelShifts> ;
    narr:childCount "43"^^xsd:integer ;
    narr:generatedFrom "c354f003fe2a54a8d5d3268a64e6f8923cccb163" ;
    narr:narration """The hub traces a multi-front shift in how work, staffing, and AI systems are organized. In Jul 2025, Scarlet and Tony framed two interlocking moves: [advisory staffing as a structural alternative to hiring](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_AdvisoryStaffingAlternativeToHiring) — monthly fees ([amount]–[amount]) replacing headcount — and [perspective-driven development inversion](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_PerspectiveDrivenDevelopmentInversion), where the AI draws on the expert's perspective rather than the expert directing the AI. Tony's [execution-to-strategy reframe](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_ExecutionToStrategyShift) (Apr 2026) extended this: AI restored IC status, making curation and strategy the scarce resource. By Mar 2026, the sales motion had split into [a demo-call prospect direct sales and Tony influence sales](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_DirectVsInfluenceSales), with [a demo-call prospect's two-step individual-asset-to-org path](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_DemoProspectTwoStepSalesPath) and a [trigger-gated equity partnership](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_DemoProspectSalesPartnership) under active pitch. [Calibration calls were reframed as billable staff-work](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_CalibrationAsStaffWork) (Jul 2025), resolving the free-conversation problem. On the technical side, Mar–Jul 2026 produced a cascade of architectural decisions: [Expert single-stream worldview](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_ExpertSingleStreamWorldview) eliminating branching, [Core Protocol vs. Internal Operations separation](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_SeparationPrincipleProtocolVsOps), [session lifetime decoupled from verification latency](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_SessionDecouplingPattern), [Fable/Opus session-boundary routing](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_FableOpusSessionBoundaryRouting), and [protocol enrollment over command](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_ProtocolEnrollmentOverCommand). Internal compensation was calibrated to company maturity via [the alignment principle](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_InternalCompensationAlignmentPrinciple) (May 2026), and the [team bottleneck reframe](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_TeamBottleneckReframe) dissolved the solo-founder framing as traction emerged.""" ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Claim_AdvisoryStaffingEconomics> ;
